{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, this dataset currently represents the most extensive collection for Chinese spelling correction tasks.",
    "• SIGHAN (Wu et al, 2013; Yu et al, 2014; Tseng et al, 2015).",
    "The SIGHAN dataset, made publicly available by scholars, serves as a resource for Chinese text correction.",
    "Presently, it encompasses three editions: SIGHAN2013, SIGHAN2014, and SIGHAN2015.",
    "The objective of the task is to evaluate the proficiency of models in Chinese spell checking, involving distinct subtasks such as detecting error positions and performing error corrections."
  ]
}